  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3582922/" class="title-link">步入屏风</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3582922"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2305565/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2305565-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2305565/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">cinekino</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-08-23"
      class="main-meta">2010-08-23 14:38:43</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3582922_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                    在读巫鸿的《重屏：中国绘画中的媒材与再现》之前，我好像已经完全忽略了我们身处的现实中“屏风”还有何种价值？它在中国古代社会是对应的是窗帘、软隔断诸如此类的概念吗？这本书的主标题直指了这个物件，而“副标题”则让人对作者的发力有所担忧，“中国绘画中的媒材与再...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">22有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_3582922_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_3582922_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





